    <h1>
      Welcome to WSO2 Cloud Services Gateway (CSG)
    </h1>

    <p>
        WSO2 Cloud Services Gateway(CSG) is a framework that can be used to expose
        a private service that is behind a firewall to the outside world in a secure and
        controllable manner. The framework consists of CSG server and the CSG Agent
        component. CSG Agent component should be installed in a service hosting
        product( such as WSO2 Application Server).
    </p>

    <p>
        WSO2 CSG is developed on top of the revolutionary
        <a href="http://wso2.org/projects/carbon">WSO2 Carbon platform</a>,
        and is based on OSGi to provide better modularity and componentization
        to your Service Oriented Architecture (SOA).
    </p>

    <p>
        You can download WSO2 CSG 1.0.0 distribution from <a href="http://dist.wso2.org/downloads/csg/">Project
        Download Page</a> and give it a try.
    </p>

